{"tid":1784653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荒謬絕倫的撐警貽笑大方","createTime":"2019-12-15T22:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T03:31:15.000Z","uid":268942,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c9843837594189725f66e0906c3af65eee483877","tid":1784653,"uid":268942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T22:15:21.000Z","msg":"香港有一個很古怪的詞彙叫「撐警」。於是「撐警集會」「撐警遊行」由之而來。一支擁有真槍實彈裝甲水炮的3萬人精銳武裝部隊，竟然要動員一班大叔大媽小丑一般地上街搖旗吶喊，醜態百出地叫囂「支持警察」，上演全世界獨一無二的荒誕劇，難道不覺得荒謬可笑麼？黑警若行得正企得穩真的「依法辦事」，堂堂正正的男子漢何需平民百姓上街撐自己？講穿了，無非是在證明香港黑警是何等的虛弱和不濟，外強中乾的形象表露無遺！"},{"pid":"c3c8d941818f9bc73c5f8bd8f674cf5445dcada3","tid":1784653,"uid":123774,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T22:30:28.000Z","msg":"撐警係不道德 低智商行為<br />\n所以得班小丑大媽搖旗助威"},{"pid":"89028e23bf1a86c211fdfa05eaf3342f94ac95d9","tid":1784653,"uid":70183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T22:30:41.000Z","msg":"搵人撑自己都搵啲好睇少少啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3227dfb0123747b3a6131bfde740b4393ab31e","tid":1784653,"uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89028e23bf1a86c211fdfa05eaf3342f94ac95d9","tid":1784653,"uid":70183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T22:30:41.000Z","msg":"搵人撑自己都搵啲好睇少少啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T23:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />前排咪揾左班四 五線暗星去撐警曱"},{"pid":"a610b2a4d6ef88a3db1d32bd51c1b71e444d2bf3","tid":1784653,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T23:56:46.000Z","msg":"外國好似真係無見過，最多得（休班警）出黎遊行講下薪酬福利"},{"pid":"d9896d77d6b5d220ce0574230f6b92747d27eb99","tid":1784653,"uid":269428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T00:30:18.000Z","msg":